    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>reserved pineapple juice </strong>and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>pineapple mayo</strong></p><p>Tip: Keep the remaining pineapple juice for your smoothies, cakes or marinades!</p>",
