    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free chick'n is starting to brown, add your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>ground allspice </strong>and<strong> soy sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for 2 min</p>",
      "order": 6,
