      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>chick'n</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks (this technique is known as ‘pulling’) then return to the pan – this is your <strong>shredded fiery meat-free chick'n</strong></p><p>Cut your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
