            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Assemble the ciabatta with a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>,<strong> </strong>a<strong> cheesy pineapple slice</strong>, the<strong> shredded fiery meat-free chick'n</strong>, another<strong> lettuce leaf</strong>, another<strong> cheesy pineapple slice</strong> and finally a dollop of <strong>pineapple mayo</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
